OL,3,CScottish Borders widower says grief
OL,4,Ccafe is helping him with his
OL,5,Cbereavement
OL,7,FA Scottish Borders widower says a
OL,8,Fgrief cafe is helping him heal
OL,9,Ffollowing the death of his wife.
OL,11,FMichael Champion has been attending a
OL,12,Fgrief cafe, at the Buccleuch Arms, in
OL,13,FSt Boswells, to help him with his
OL,14,Floss. The group aims to create a
OL,15,Fwelcoming space for those navigating
OL,16,Fthe emotions of grief.
