OL,7,FThe informal meets enable individuals
OL,8,Fto share memories, feelings, and
OL,9,Fexperiences with people who are also
OL,10,Fdealing with the loss of their loved
OL,11,Fones.
OL,13,FThe space creates an alternative to
OL,14,Fcounselling and therapy, offering
OL,15,Fanother form of bereavement support.
