OL,3,CScottish Borders widower says grief
OL,4,Ccafe is helping him with his
OL,5,Cbereavement
OL,7,FMartin said: "I had nobody to talk
OL,8,Fabout grief. I've made so many friends
OL,9,Fnow, and it helps me on my journey. It
OL,10,Fdoesn't help me to forget because it's
OL,11,Falways a presence on your mind every
OL,12,Fminute of the day.
OL,14,F"There's tears and laughter, it's not
OL,15,Falways about grief and it just
OL,16,Felevates what we're feeling, bringing
OL,17,Fsome hope that there is a way forward."
