OL,3,CScottish Borders widower says grief
OL,4,Ccafe is helping him with his
OL,5,Cbereavement
OL,7,FThe group relies on the support of
OL,8,Fpeople who are experiencing similar
OL,9,Femotions. The cafes are free to attend
OL,10,Fand home-baking, tray-bakes, tea, and
OL,11,Fcoffee are all provided.
OL,13,FThe bereavement groups now support
OL,14,Fmore than fifty people across the
OL,15,FScottish Borders.
OL,17,FShelagh Hogg lost her husband Bruce,
OL,18,Ftwenty months ago, she describes the
OL,19,Fsupport group as a "lifeline".
