OL,4,Ccafe is helping him with his
OL,5,Cbereavement
OL,7,FShe said: "I know other people have
OL,8,Fsaid the same. I don't know how I
OL,9,Fwould have managed without it.
OL,11,F"It's time to just relax and not have
OL,12,Fthat 'everything's okay' mask on, and
OL,13,Fif you get upset it's fine, everybody
OL,14,Funderstands and there's no pressure.
