OL,3,CScottish Borders widower says grief
OL,4,Ccafe is helping him with his
OL,5,Cbereavement
OL,7,F"People's lives move on and you feel
OL,8,Flike your life comes to a total
OL,9,Fstandstill. Having that space in time
OL,10,Fto able to say whatever you want to
OL,11,Fsay and everything's private and
OL,12,Fconfidential, it's a safe space for
OL,13,Feverybody.
OL,15,F"I kind of feel his presence, it's
OL,16,Falmost like a date with Bruce, that's
OL,17,Fhow I've explained it to people
OL,18,Fbefore. It's time to be able to speak
OL,19,Fabout him... it's time to reflect and
OL,20,Fjust tell people about your person."
